d just outside the hotel is a pedestrian walkway leading to both resorts. Close to the complex, there are many restaurants, cafes, bars and shops.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Rooms open to balconies. Televisions come with satellite channels and pay movies. Wireless Internet access is provided along with direct-dial phones and in-room safes. Bathrooms include bathrobes, slippers, makeup/shaving mirrors, and bidets. Separate sitting areas, minibars, and air conditioning are also included. A nightly turndown service and housekeeping are provided. Amenities available on request include wake-up calls. Rooms are accessible via exterior corridors.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>From the exquisite architecture and design of the main entrance, with its magnificent stained-glass dome, to the beautiful gardens with numerous exotic plants and trees, the Jardines De Nivaria stands out as something extra special.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>Whether it s breakfast on the terrace or dinner in the buffet or a la carte restaurants, the cuisine in the Jardines De Nivaria is excellent. The relaxing atmosphere extends into the evening when guests unwind with cocktails and drinks in one of the hotel bars.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>OutdoorPool</Code><Text>Outdoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Hairdresser</Code><Text>Hairdresser</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Am